library(ggplot2)
library(stats)

gen_data <- function(num){
  x <- seq(from = 0.1, to = num*0.1, by = 0.1)
  e <- rnorm(num)

  y_expected <- 0.6*x +sin(3*x)
  y_observed <- y_expected + e
  
  return(list(y_expected,y_observed,x))
}
train <- gen_data(100)
y_expected_train <- train[[1]]
y_observed_train <- train[[2]]
x_train <- train[[3]]

test <- gen_data(100)
y_expected_test <- test[[1]]
y_observed_test <- test[[2]]
x_test <- test[[3]]

test_pred <- gen_data(100)
y_expected_test_pred <- test_pred[[1]]
y_observed_test_pred <- test_pred[[2]]
x_test_pred <- test_pred[[3]]
splines_pred_error_simulator <- function(df, train, test){
  
  # Variable Definitions
  y_expected_train <- train[[1]]
  y_observed_train <- train[[2]]
  x_train <- train[[3]]
  y_expected_test <- test[[1]]
  y_observed_test <- test[[2]]
  x_test <- test[[3]]
  
  # Fit Training Data
  res <- smooth.spline(x_train, y_observed_train, df=df)
  
  
  # Fit
  fit <- predict(res,x_train)$y
  
  # Training Errors
  ss_train_errors <-  sum((y_observed_train - fit)^2)
  
  # Training Bias
  ss_train_bias <- sum((y_expected_train - fit)^2)
  
  # Training Variance
  train_variance <- var(fit)
  
  
  # Prediction 
  prediction <- predict(res,x_test)$y
  
  # Prediction Errors
  ss_pred_errors <-  sum((y_observed_test - prediction)^2)
  
  # Prediction Bias
  ss_pred_bias <- sum((y_expected_test - prediction)^2)
  
  # Training Variance
  pred_variance <- var(prediction)

  
  returns <- list(ss_train_errors,ss_train_bias,train_variance,
                  ss_pred_errors,ss_pred_bias,pred_variance)
  
  return(returns)
}
df_seq = seq(2,30,1)

ss_train_errors_list <- list()
ss_train_bias_list <- list()
train_variance_list <- list()
ss_pred_errors_list <- list()
ss_pred_bias_list <- list()
pred_variance_list <- list()

for (df in df_seq) {
  returns <- splines_pred_error_simulator(df, train, test)
  
  ss_train_errors_list <- append(ss_train_errors_list,returns[[1]])
  ss_train_bias_list   <- append(ss_train_bias_list  ,returns[[2]])
  train_variance_list  <- append(train_variance_list ,returns[[3]])
  ss_pred_errors_list  <- append(ss_pred_errors_list ,returns[[4]])
  ss_pred_bias_list    <- append(ss_pred_bias_list   ,returns[[5]])
  pred_variance_list   <- append(pred_variance_list  ,returns[[6]])
  
}

ss_train_errors_list <- unlist(ss_train_errors_list)
ss_train_bias_list   <- unlist(ss_train_bias_list)
train_variance_list  <- unlist(train_variance_list)
ss_pred_errors_list  <- unlist(ss_pred_errors_list)
ss_pred_bias_list    <- unlist(ss_pred_bias_list)
pred_variance_list   <- unlist(pred_variance_list)

ss_train_errors_df <- data.frame(df = df_seq, y = ss_train_errors_list)
ss_train_bias_df   <- data.frame(df = df_seq, y = ss_train_bias_list)
train_variance_df  <- data.frame(df = df_seq, y = train_variance_list)
ss_pred_errors_df  <- data.frame(df = df_seq, y = ss_pred_errors_list)
ss_pred_bias_df    <- data.frame(df = df_seq, y = ss_pred_bias_list)
pred_variance_df   <- data.frame(df = df_seq, y = pred_variance_list)

# Errors
ggplot(data=ss_train_errors_df,aes(x=df_seq,y=y),colour='green') + geom_line() + 
  geom_line(data=ss_pred_errors_df,colour='red') 

# Bias
ggplot(data=ss_train_bias_df,aes(x=df_seq,y=y),colour='green') + geom_line() + 
  geom_line(data=ss_pred_bias_df,colour='red') 

# Variance
ggplot(data=train_variance_df,aes(x=df_seq,y=y),colour='green') + geom_line() + 
  geom_line(data=pred_variance_df,colour='red')

library(tree)
data = read.csv2("/Users/maherp/Desktop/Universitaet/Goettingen/3_Semester/Advanced_Statistical_Learning/tutorial_4/data.txt", sep=",", col.names = list("1","2","3","4","5","6","7","8","class"))
error_list <- list()
error_sum_list <- list()

for(i in seq(ncol(data)-1)) {       # for-loop over columns
  
  tree_model <- tree(data$class ~ data[,i], split = "gini")
  pred <- predict(tree_model,data)
  
  error = as.numeric(data$class == round(pred))
  
  error_sum <- sum(error)
  
  error_sum_list <- append(error_sum_list,error_sum)
  error_list[i] <- error
  
}
